<br>
I'm a 60 necro with lifeburn.  Multiple necros can cast lifeburn and have it affect a mob.  The buff doesn't go onto the mob it just goes onto you.  Why it cannot/doesn't crit is left up to VI.  Of course I'd like to see a multiplier on it but that's for obvious reasons.  So yes, a group of necros could do the same ... do a &quot;/who all 60 necro&quot; on your server and if the number is less than 25 then you can forget a similar thread being posted ever.<br>
<br>
I love the idea of a stack of wizards roaming the lands owning stuff up.  It's just neat.  Start off weaklings and end up like gods ... gotta love that, that's what we all had in mind for wizards in the fantasy genre.<br>
<br>
